HEADWORD: 90
<hw>90</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>one more than eighty-nine
and one less than ninety-one; denoting a quantity consisting of ninety
items or units; -- representing the number ninety as Arabic
numerals</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ninety, xc</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

